"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-showbiz-tv-radio-2005722-bbc-antiques-roadshow-olympic-torch\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"An Antiques Roadshow guest was in disbelief when he discovered the whopping value for his unbelievable memento from the 1988 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a recent visit to Pollok Park, Glasgow, the belovedBBCseries saw experts, including Jamie Russell, appraising unique items brought by members of the public.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pollok_Country_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pollok Park\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pollok_Country_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pollok_Country_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 175, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999889419088, \"rank\": 9.893734241465468e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999976776705034, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamie Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ever-knowledgeable Russell was taken aback when veteran journalist Gavin Bell presented an Olympic torch, having not anticipated such an iconic item would emerge from the day's collection.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gavin Bell\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Andresen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With astonishment, Russell said: \\\"Before I came here today to the Roadshow, I had a long list of items in my head that I thought I might see that would appear out of boxes and bags in front of me.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But one of them was definitely not an Olympic torch.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wonder if you can tell us how you came to own this.\\\"\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell, with a hint of nostalgia, recounted his journey: \\\"When I was a young lad, I was an 800 metres runner with a Glasgow club.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999889419088, \"rank\": 9.893734241465468e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, of course, as a boy, I dreamed of running in the Olympics one day.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then eventually, the dream came true in a way I'd never have expected.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was posted to South Korea in advance of the 1988 Games for The Times.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999998870991994, \"rank\": 7.242706882437084e-08, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so while I was there, I met a couple of young English lads who'd been appointed to do the public relations for the torch relay.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they found out about my athletic background and invited me to carry the torch on the first day it arrived in Korea.\\\"\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"score\": 0.5701383184518048, \"rank\": 0.7467963226981411, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Bell quipped that the snap of him holding the torch was \\\"good publicity\\\" for the Olympics and even landed on the front page of The Times.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999999913413831, \"rank\": 8.658578074481453e-09, \"text\": \"The Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russell expressed his delight, saying: \\\"I mean, it's fantastic.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's really amazing to see one here in rainy Glasgow.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999889419088, \"rank\": 9.893734241465468e-09, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And what's also great is not only do we know from how it looks what it is but it tells us right here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He pointed out the inscription, which revealed the torch's journey from Olympia, Greece to the Olympic Stadium in Seoul in 1988.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia, Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia, Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia,_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 2139, \"end\": 2144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.999866167523694, \"rank\": 0.00013383277162821934, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russell admired the design, highlighting the \\\"scrolled and gilt leather handle\\\", the \\\"distinctive Olympic rings\\\", and the \\\"crossing dragons and mythical figures\\\" symbolising unity between East and West.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2155, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After assessing the torch, he estimated its value at auction to be around \\u00a31,500 to \\u00a32,500.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell's reaction was one of astonishment, his eyes widening and jaw dropping as he exclaimed: \\\"Really?!\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", followed by \\\"Gee whizz!\\\"\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Russell nodded in agreement, saying: \\\"And it's such an iconic item.\\\"\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2585, \"end\": 2592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell jokingly remarked: \\\"Well I can not accept money for it, I am an amateur!\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", with Russell concurring: \\\"One to hold on to.\\\"\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4750542327811154e-12, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Antiques Roadshow is available to watch on BBC One and BBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9191647852255307e-37, \"text\": \"Antiques Roadshow\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\"}, {\"begin\": 2825, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0134064241176935e-21, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 2837, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999986636234842, \"rank\": 9.593232437585047e-07, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2841, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"